Addon.Barcode.GetLocalVersion()

Description

Returns the version info of the files DynamicBarcode.dll and DynamicBarcodex64.dll which are installed on the local machine.

Syntax

.Addon.Barcode.GetLocalVersion();

Parameters

None.

Return value

<string>
The result string represents the version of the barcode files installed locally.

See also

Addon.Barcode.Download()
